{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_KEI_620.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1e,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Let's take a short rest around here. You're starting to get tired, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, bingo. I'm so thirsty."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cb,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I guess I'll enjoy a smoke as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Another cigarette?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I can't live without them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Do they taste good...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cf,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "They do, without a doubt."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Heh, cigarettes and alchemy might be somewhat similar for me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Both have their own peculiarities, but they each beckon to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oh, do you remember the talk we had on the bridge at Hornheim?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Yes, about the sins that past alchemists have committed. Of course I remember."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "It's going to help save Nio, so I just can't consider alchemy to be something evil."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy itself is neither good nor evil. However, it's up to humans and how they use it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Putting it differently, I suppose you could say that humans, as a whole, are \"evil.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Th-That's not true! All the people I know are nice, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I can't even imagine doing evil things with alchemy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Keith, maybe you're thinking too much on the bad parts..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "If you continue to master alchemy, you'll eventually understand."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Most people just put on the mask of a saint. You just haven't realized that yet."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "You don't even know what people are saying behind your back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "That's not true!<CR>You're wrong, Mr. Keith..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Goodness, you're more stubborn than you look. No, maybe it's your youth..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "There's no need for you to venture out to discover this, but...if you insist, I'll prove it to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I'll show you the malice of humans that still remains today."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "It's there, in a place across the sky from Hornheim. Head over there."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "And there, you'll learn just how true my words are."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "From Hornheim? The sky...? That seems kinda scary..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "You can't help but go.<CR>You've said so yourself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "And if you're an alchemist, it'll be somewhat meaningful for you to see it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1d0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Now, we should get going."
        }
    ]
}